- Data users who rely on the department's statistical services;
- Statistical analysts and experts familiar with the department's processes and methodologies;
- Policy-makers responsible for developing and implementing statistical policies and regulations;
- Researchers who specialize in specific areas or topics related to the department's responsibilities;
- Administrative personnel involved in managing and coordinating the statistical programmatic components;
- External partners and consultants engaged in providing expertise or assistance to the department;

